                Zero-dependency asynchronous HTTP request queue using Bun JS and Sqlite.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <a class="font-bold text-black" href="https://conwaygameoflife-production.up.railway.app/" target="_blank">
                Conway's Game of Life
